schools.name: Veterans Park Academy For The Arts

data.description: Beautiful two-story house with space for 5 rooms and garage! Perfect for a large family. The main floor has a private living room and great room that opens to the dining room and kitchen. The second floor features the owner's suite with full bath and walk-in closet. Also upstairs there are 2 more bedrooms, a loft and another full bathroom! In addition, the house has: Solar panels. Electricity and water connection for a mobile home. Security cameras A gazebo equipped with curtains, colored lights, ceiling fan and plastic floor with imitation wood. A modern kitchen on the terrace. A space enabled for pets.
